    "iCloud 同步": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud Sync"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "iCloud 同步將於下次開啟 App 後生效。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud sync will take effect the next time you open the app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "iCloud 同步預設關閉；開啟後將備份至你的 iCloud。通知權限請於系統設定調整。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud sync is off by default; when on, your data is backed up to your iCloud. Adjust notification permissions in system Settings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」今天到期，記得處理。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“%@” expires today — remember to use it."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」將被刪除，此操作無法復原。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“%@” will be deleted. This cannot be undone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
